{"id": 2746, "genre": 1000, "title": "线上聊天，你觉得哪些细节能看出对方说的是真情实感？", "description": "哈哈哈可能是假笑，对方一堆哈哈哈哈哈中间“顺手”打错一个字才是真的很好笑。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 11354, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190119123902x8Tgy3BKS1OAfcDd.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-21T17:00:38Z", "questions": [{"id": 5254, "title": "线上聊天，你觉得哪些细节能看出对方说的是真情实感？", "content": "聊天时你都会用哪些方法来表现真实情绪？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 323473, "content": "一句话是一字一顿发过来的", "image": "img/option/option/20190119102917q9h76WpQl0w1sNTO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323474, "content": "用了不少于两种语言，absolutely 是这样 desu", "image": "img/option/option/201901191034398RV1ejx3L7q2ZmCU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323475, "content": "给文字配上了符合情境的表情包", "image": "img/option/option/20190119104309iVoyt9Pv0shUlcBY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323476, "content": "发来一串感叹号/句号/省略号", "image": "img/option/option/2019011910433680PjQT91rWmRKMAG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323477, "content": "夹杂一些错别字，比如哈哈哈或、hhhhjjhhhh 啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20190121104421WJGlTRaXLri6p0qo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323478, "content": "煞有介事用了正确的表情符号，每段话后边还有句号", "image": "img/option/option/20190119110107oKaf4Xt5SxieZm3s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323479, "content": "声明自己是“zqsg”", "image": "img/option/option/20190121111552KDtd7bs48m12ugOl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 323480, "content": "以上都没有，我都是从上下文和文字内容判断的", "image": "img/option/option/20190119110255I27HUSQqbmdB8AgW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}